column2: SELECT u.up_name as [name], x.objID, s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid, p.z, s.dered_u, s.dered_r, p.rest_ug, p.rest_gr FROM #upload u JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id JOIN PhotoTag pp ON pp.objID = x.objID JOIN Photoz p ON p.objID = x.objID JOIN SpecPhotoAll AS s ON s.objID = p.objID ORDER by x.up_id
